## Med resource endpoints

## get user med log by id
GET  http://localhost:3000/api/med/2

## modify med instruction
POST   http://localhost:3000/api/med/2
Content-Type: application/json
{
  "user_id": "2",
  "name": "QuickIns",
  "bs_l1": "8",
  "d_l1": "3",
  "bs_l2": "4",
  "ds_l2": "2",
  "note": "add 1IU every third bd value after 8",
}



